Common.Highlight.Common.Text: NEARBY ASC NAVAL SHIP BUILDING YARD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer For Sale or Lease, 3 Brand New Office/Warehouses located in Largs North. 

- Brand new opportunity to occupy a new building nearby ASC Naval Ship Building Yards
- Warehousing spaces available from 294sqm* to 326sqm*
- 18 carparks total available 
- Due for completion Q4 2021
- Quality amenities and finishes

WHS 1 - 326sqm* incl 60sqm* ground floor office & amenities as well as 1st floor mezzanine
WHS 2 - 294sqm* incl 58sqm* ground floor office & amenities as well as 1st floor mezzanine
WHS 3 - 303sqm* incl 60sqm* ground floor office & amenities as well as 1st floor mezzanine

*approximately

Please contact the listing agents for more information or to arrange an inspection

Marina Adelaide is a perfectly positioned business park in the Largs Bay/Osbourne area. Located 5 minutes from the heart of Port Adelaide and just minutes from the Osbourne shipping precinct and approximately 500 metres from Victoria Road. 

With a myriad of options available, the facility has options for the corporate office user to government to the SME to groups seeking warehouse space. Ample on-site carparking is available for all users including visitors. 

Tenancies 2 and 3 combined offer a total of 635 square metres that was completed by the SA Government. The space is afforded with a full fitout including furniture, data cabling and terrific security.  Split over the 2 levels with lift access to level 1, the tenancy is available for immediate occupation.

Tenancies 4,5,6 are suitable for multiple uses including showroom, office and storage. With areas from 154sqm to 712ssqm and the ability to sub-divide, the owners are prepared to work with groups on their requirements. 

Also available is an external self-contained warehouse of 600sqm what was previously used by the Fisheries department. Quality services and fully secure.

*approx.
